dc_title_s: Афины и Пирей (J-34-72,84) : Греция, номы Аттика, Пирей (J-34-72,84)
dc_description_s: Relief shown by 10 meter contour interval, spot heights. Depths shown by 10 meter contour interval and soundings. Sistema koordinat 1942 g. Military topographic map showing numbered government, military, transportation, and industrial facilities. Ancilary map: skhema linii metropolitena [map of the subway lines]. Includes text, indexes, and sheet-assembly diagrams. "Sostavleno v 1973g. Ispravleno po materialam na 1979,1981gg." "Sistema koordinat 1942 g." Sheets numbered: List 1 [northern] -- List 2 [southern]. Former security classification in margins: Sekretno. "I-18/1 XI-84-K. I-18/2 XI-84-K." "Составлено в 1973г. Исправлено по материалам на 1979,1981гг." "Система координат 1942 г." Sheets numbered: Лист 1 [northern] -- Лист 2 [southern]. Former security classification in margins: Секретно. "И-18/1 XI-84-К. И-18/2 XI-84-К." One map in two sheets. Relief shown by 10 m. contour interval and spot heights. Depths shown by 10 m.contour interval and soundings. Sistema koordinat 1942 g. Ancilary map: skhema linii metropolitena [subway line]. Map shows numbered government, military, transportation, and industrial facilities. "Sostavleno v 1973g.
